title: KrissyJaycee2
body:
You walk up to Krissy and Jaycee.
<<Speaking Krissy>>Heyyy!
<<Speaking Jaycee>>What's up!

[[It's good!|201w]]
[[Great!|201w]]

title: 201w
body:
<<Speaking Jaycee>>Oh my god aren't you like so excited for the party tonight?

[[I can't wait!!|301w]]
[[It's going to be amazingggg.|301w]]

title: 301w
body:
<<Speaking Jaycee>>I know, right? I can't wait either!
<<Speaking Krissy>>We were just talking about what mixers to bring and everything.
<<Speaking Krissy>>Oh, by the way, what mixers do you think we should buy? I was just telling Ellie what to buy.

[[Coke.|401w]]
[[Um, more alcohol, haha.|402w]]

title: 402w
body:
<<Speaking Krissy>>Hahaha, don't worry, we've got plenty.
<<Speaking Krissy>>We're gonna need something else, though.
<<Speaking Jaycee>>Oh, you should get lemonade! Lemonade is so good with vodka.
<<Speaking Krissy>>Lemonade is way too sugary, Jaycee, haha.
<<Speaking Krissy>>I don't want my teeth to get yellow.
<<Speaking Jaycee>>Oh yea, you're totally right, I guess I didn't think about that. You're right, lemonade is disgusting.
<<Speaking Krissy>>Well, I think I'll tell her to grab orange juice. There's a lot of low-sugar orange juice.
<<Speaking Krissy>>I'll be right back.
She turns around and leaves the conversation.

[[So, how's it going?|501w]]
[[What's up?|501w]]

title: 501w
body:
<<Speaking Jaycee>>It's great!! 
Jaycee giggles forcefully.
<<Speaking Jaycee>>I still can't believe we're here! It's so amazing.

[[Yea, it's great!|601w]]
[[I know, it's like, pretty overwhelming, haha.|602w]]

title: 602w
body:
<<Speaking Jaycee>>I know, it's like, crazy.
<<Speaking Jaycee>>But everyone is so nice and welcoming, I'm like, so comfortable around them. 
<<Speaking Jaycee>>I've spent all morning thinking about how great the party's going to be and what it's going to be like. 
<<Speaking Jaycee>>What do you think is going to happen?
